<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">د ر ز:</span> <span class="c2">(الدَّرْزُ)</span> وَاحِدُ <span class="c2">(دُرُوزِ)</span> الثَّوْبِ فَارِسِيٌّ مُعَرَّبٌ،<span class="c5"> وَيُقَالُ لِلْقَمْلِ وَالصِّئْبَانِ:</span> بَنَاتُ الدُّرُوزِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>